data.description:
Welcome to 6940 Albaneen Court, a residence nestled in a peaceful corner of Charlotte, NC. Boasting 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a serene backyard, this home offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless charm.
Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home offers easy access to shopping destinations, dining options, and recreational amenities, ensuring a lifestyle of convenience and enjoyment for the whole family. Don't miss your chance to experience the best of Charlotte living at 6940 Albaneen Court.
